# Slide 2 – Problem Statement

Earthquakes occur every day across the world and generate large amounts of seismic data. Analyzing this information helps identify high-risk regions, understand earthquake trends, and support disaster preparedness. This project transforms raw earthquake data into meaningful insights using data analytics and visualization.

---

# Slide 3 – Project Objectives

* Collect earthquake data from the USGS Earthquake API.
* Clean and preprocess raw data.
* Store processed data in a MySQL database.
* Perform SQL-based analysis.
* Build an interactive Streamlit dashboard.
* Generate actionable insights from global earthquake data.

