# Slide 9 – Key Insights

* Most recorded earthquakes occur at shallow depths.
* Moderate-magnitude earthquakes are more common than very high-magnitude events.
* Earthquake frequency varies across years and geographic regions.
* Some countries experience significantly higher seismic activity.
* Interactive dashboards improve exploration of earthquake trends and support decision-making.

